Notes: Required field for final wellbeing check. Maps to medical_how_are_you_feeling in Typeform but uses different field name (final_feeling vs medical_how_are_you_feeling). Options: fine, shaken, minor_pain, significant_pain, emergency. Triggers medical alerts based on selection.
ISO timestamp when page 12 completed. Generated by JavaScript. Not stored in database - used for tracking completion in sessionStorage only.
